# Environment Strategy & Secrets Layout
*This is the updated `.env.example` structure for Production Readiness.*

```env
# POOOL Environment Configuration

# ----------------------------------------
# 1. CORE APPLICATION & ENVIRONMENT
# ----------------------------------------
APP_ENV=development # Options: development | staging | production
BASE_URL=http://localhost:8888
SERVER_HOST=0.0.0.0
SERVER_PORT=8888
RUST_LOG=info # or warn/error/debug

# ----------------------------------------
# 2. DATABASE & CACHING
# ----------------------------------------
DATABASE_URL=postgres://martin@localhost/poool
# Recommended caching layer for session storage and frequent queries
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379/0

# ----------------------------------------
# 3. SECURITY & CRYPTOGRAPHY
# ----------------------------------------
# Master key used for JWT signing and session validation
# Generate using: `openssl rand -base64 32`
JWT_SECRET=super_secret_placeholder
# Key used to encrypt sensitive financial data (like bank account details) in the database
# Generate using: `openssl rand -base64 32`
ENCRYPTION_KEY=super_secret_placeholder
# Strict CORS policies for production deployment
CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://localhost:8888,https://poool.com,https://www.poool.com

# ----------------------------------------
# 4. EXTERNAL AUTHENTICATION (OAUTH2)
# ----------------------------------------
# Google: https://console.cloud.google.com -> APIs & Services -> Credentials
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=

# Facebook: https://developers.facebook.com -> My Apps
FACEBOOK_APP_ID=
FACEBOOK_APP_SECRET=

# ----------------------------------------
# 5. KYC & COMPLIANCE (DIDIT.ME)
# ----------------------------------------
# Used for automated user verification during onboarding. Falls back to manual review if empty.
DIDIT_API_KEY=
DIDIT_WORKFLOW_ID=
DIDIT_WEBHOOK_SECRET=

# ----------------------------------------
# 6. COMMUNICATION (EMAILS/RESEND)
# ----------------------------------------
# Traffic Creator ecosystem relies on Resend API for transactional and marketing emails
RESEND_API_KEY=
EMAIL_FROM_ADDRESS=noreply@poool.com
EMAIL_SUPPORT_ADDRESS=support@poool.com

# ----------------------------------------
# 7. METRICS & ERROR MONITORING
# ----------------------------------------
# Sentry DSN for tracking application exceptions
SENTRY_DSN=
```
